{"tid":673254,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"原來打尖反而唔會俾人鬧","createTime":"2018-05-21T16:23:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-21T16:38:13.000Z","uid":105614,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9fdb589c33c58fca42a2865fc117933f535bba78","tid":673254,"uid":105614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T16:23:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁嘅，今日就諗住同班姊妹一齊去睇戲啦<br />\n排隊買飛嘅時候我前面係個應該大概9歲10歲嘅妹妹，原本佢同佢媽一齊排 中途佢阿媽就行開可能去廁所，係呢個時候有條友越行越近sip下sip下咁過黎想打尖，我就出聲同佢講話係排我前面個妹妹先，唔該去後面排隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後竟然佢仲夠膽咁多人睇住情況下話佢係排先，到佢阿媽返黎問咩事之後，個老母竟然屌返我轉頭話 我個女俾人打尖咪打尖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關你咩事，等陣你兩個咁講嘢嚇親我個女點算<br />\n<br />\n之後我一句應返佢，我話 你估你個女俾人打尖淨係得佢俾人打尖？依家我都俾人打埋尖喔 我出聲有咩問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後佢收咗皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30799b1f119655c715a36b9d8dadb605c41051da","tid":673254,"uid":70439,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T16:26:58.000Z","msg":"唔識教女就代佢教，係佢老母面前屌撚到佢撻皮，咁撚鍾意俾人打尖，唔見你拎塊閪出黎比人免費屌下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fd6b80f0a210228011b3d398d3711ecf4e4e3f5","tid":673254,"uid":6385,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T16:33:01.000Z","msg":"咁佢個女比人強奸，關人咩事？"},{"pid":"ddb7d75ee2f95f6eb852e15966a9aad3db910180","tid":673254,"uid":63588,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"2fd6b80f0a210228011b3d398d3711ecf4e4e3f5","tid":673254,"uid":6385,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T16:33:01.000Z","msg":"咁佢個女比人強奸，關人咩事？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T16:34:50.000Z","msg":"You took it too far"},{"pid":"9f26a9546b96ab438a4aa24d6f7d15ad4ed2b366","tid":673254,"uid":126554,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pi